com.teamdev.jxbrowser.chromium

Class Browser

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.teamdev.jxbrowser.chromium.Browser

  • public class Browser
extends java.lang.Object
    Represents web browser control based on Chromium engine. It can be used to load web page, local HTML file, access DOM and JavaScript of loaded HTML document, listen to the events such as status change, loading started, loading finished, loading failed, document title changed, JavaScript console messages, etc.

    Browser allows displaying modern HTML5/CSS3/JavaScript web pages, PDF documents, PPAPI Flash content if appropriate PPAPI Chromium plugin is installed.

    Each Browser instance is running in separate native process and communicates with Java process via Inter-Process-Communication (IPC) bridge. If Browser instance is disposed unexpectedly in native process (e.g. due to crash in Flash plugin), it will not affect Java application. The application will continue working.

    When you don't need to use Browser instance you must dispose it using the dispose() method to free allocated memory and resources. Once you dispose Browser instance, you cannot use it anymore, so if you call its method after you dispose Browser instance, you will get IllegalStateException error.

    By default Browser instance displays popup windows, JavaScript dialogs such as alert, confirm, prompt, file open/save dialogs, print settings dialog, etc. To modify default behavior feel free to register your own implementation of corresponding handlers.
    表示基于Chromium引擎的Web浏览器控件。它可用于加载网页，本地HTML文件，访问已加载HTML文档的DOM和JavaScript，侦听状态更改，加载开始，加载完成，加载失败，文档标题更改，JavaScript控制台消息等事件。如果安装了适当的PPAPI Chromium插件，浏览器将允许显示现代HTML5 / CSS3 / JavaScript网页，PDF文档，PPAPI Flash内容。每个浏览器实例都在单独的本机进程中运行，并通过进程间通信（IPC）桥与Java进程进行通信。如果浏览器实例在本机进程中意外处置（例如，由于Flash插件崩溃），则不会影响Java应用程序。该应用程序将继续运行。当不需要使用浏览器实例时，必须使用dispose（）方法将其释放，以释放分配的内存和资源。处置浏览器实例后，将无法再使用它，因此，如果处置处置浏览器实例后调用其方法，则会收到IllegalStateException错误。默认情况下，浏览器实例显示弹出窗口，JavaScript对话框，例如警报，确认，提示，文件打开/保存对话框，打印设置对话框等。要修改默认行为，请随时注册自己的相应处理程序实现。

        Blocks current thread execution, invokes the given task that must initiate web page loading, and waits until the main frame of the web page is loaded completely or until the timeout is reached.

        Use this method when you need to perform some action that initiates web page loading and you have to wait until the web page is loaded completely. If the given task doesn't cause web page loading or the web page loading has been failed for some reasons, then this method will block current thread execution until timeout is reached (by default 45 seconds).

        Important: Use this method for loading web pages only.

        Parameters:

      • dispose

        public void dispose()
        Disposes the current Browser instance and waits until all pending Browser tasks are completed.

        For example, if you call the Browser.executeJavaScriptAndReturnValue() method that takes 10 seconds to get return value from JavaScript and in another thread you dispose Browser instance using Browser.dispose() method, the method will block current thread execution and wait until Browser.executeJavaScriptAndReturnValue() method has finished its execution.

        When Browser instance is being disposed you cannot invoke its methods. If you do it, you will get IllegalStateException exception.
        处置当前的浏览器实例，并等待所有未完成的浏览器任务完成。例如，如果调用需要10秒钟才能从JavaScript获取返回值的Browser.executeJavaScriptAndReturnValue（）方法，并且在另一个线程中使用Browser.dispose（）方法处置Browser实例，则该方法将阻止当前线程执行并等待，直到Browser .executeJavaScriptAndReturnValue（）方法已完成执行。处理浏览器实例时，无法调用其方法。如果这样做，您将获得IllegalStateException异常。
        See Also:
        isDisposed()

      • dispose

        public boolean dispose(boolean checkBeforeUnload)
        Tries to unload current document and if unload is not declined, disposes current Browser instance and waits until all pending Browser tasks are completed.

        If checkBeforeUnload parameter is true and current document has the window.onbeforeunload() method implemented, Browser engine will initiate displaying before unload confirmation dialog to ask user whether current document should be closed and current thread execution will be blocked until the DialogHandler.onBeforeUnload(UnloadDialogParams) method is completed. By default the {@link DialogHandler#onBeforeUnload(UnloadDialogParams)} method is executed in UI thread. Therefore you must invoke the dispose() method in non-UI thread to avoid deadlock.

        If user cancelles closing current document, the Browser instance will not be disposed. If current document doesn't have the window.onbeforeunload() method implemented or user confirms closing current document, the Browser instance will be disposed.

        Note, that if the DialogHandler field of current Browser instance is set to null and current document does have the window.onbeforeunload() method implemented, the Browser instance will not be disposed.

        Note, that Browser instance will always be disposed if customer haven't performed any actions with document before this method is invoked, e.g. focused, clicked, etc.

        If current Browser instance is disposed, does nothing and returns true.
        尝试卸载当前文档，如果没有拒绝卸载，请处置当前的Browser实例，并等待所有未完成的Browser任务完成。如果checkBeforeUnload参数为true并且当前文档已实现window.onbeforeunload（）方法，则浏览器引擎将在卸载确认对话框前启动显示，询问用户是否应关闭当前文档，并且当前线程执行将被阻塞，直到DialogHandler.onBeforeUnload（UnloadDialogParams） ）方法完成。默认情况下，{@ link DialogHandler＃onBeforeUnload（UnloadDialogParams）}方法在UI线程中执行。因此，必须在非UI线程中调用dispose（）方法，以避免死锁。如果用户取消关闭当前文档，则将不会处理Browser实例。如果当前文档没有实现window.onbeforeunload（）方法，或者用户确认关闭当前文档，则将处置Browser实例。请注意，如果当前浏览器实例的DialogHandler字段设置为null，并且当前文档的确实现了window.onbeforeunload（）方法，则将不处理浏览器实例。请注意，如果客户在调用此方法之前未对文档执行任何操作，则将始终释放Browser实例。集中，单击等。如果已处理当前的Browser实例，则不执行任何操作并返回true。
        Parameters:
        checkBeforeUnload - determines if Browser engine dispatches the beforeUnload event before and waits for result before disposing current Browser instance. -确定浏览器引擎是否在分派当前浏览器实例之前分派beforeUnload事件并等待结果。
        Returns:
        true if current browser instance is disposed. 当前的浏览器实例是否已处置。
        Since:
        6.15
        See Also:
        dispose(), isDisposed(), setDialogHandler(DialogHandler)

      • getRenderProcessInfo

        public RenderProcessInfo getRenderProcessInfo()
        Returns information about Chromium render process associated with the current Browser instance. When Chromium loads a new web page, it creates a new render process where DOM and JavaScript are running. This render process can be terminated by Chromium engine when a new web page with different domain is loaded. So, this method can return different render process information.

        The information about render process is collected at the moment of the method invocation. You must call this method again if you need to get the up to date information.

        返回有关与当前Browser实例关联的Chromium渲染过程的信息。 Chromium加载新网页时，会在运行DOM和JavaScript的地方创建一个新的呈现过程。当加载具有不同域的新网页时，此渲染过程可由Chromium引擎终止。因此，此方法可以返回不同的渲染过程信息。在方法调用时收集有关渲染过程的信息。如果您需要获取最新信息，则必须再次调用此方法。
        Returns:
        returns an object that provides information about render process. Returns null if there's no render process associated with the current Browser instance. 返回提供有关渲染过程信息的对象。如果当前浏览器实例没有关联的渲染过程，则返回。
        Since:
        6.8

      • setCustomStyleSheet

        public void setCustomStyleSheet(java.lang.String customStyleSheet)
        Injects the given customStyleSheet string that represents a custom style sheet (CSS) into every HTML document loaded in this instance. The given CSS will be applied during loading HTML document. If the document is already loaded, the CSS will not be applied. The document must be reloaded to apply the CSS.

        If CSS property defined in the given customStyleSheet string already exists on the loaded HTML document, then the existing CSS property won't be overriden. The CSS properties defined in the given customStyleSheet string will be applied only if these properties aren't defined on the loaded document.

        To reset CSS pass empty string as parameter.

        将表示自定义样式表（CSS）的给定customStyleSheet字符串插入此实例中加载的每个HTML文档中。给定的CSS将在加载HTML文档期间应用。如果文档已经加载，则CSS将不会应用。必须重新加载文档才能应用CSS。如果在给定的customStyleSheet字符串中定义的CSS属性已在加载的HTML文档上存在，则不会覆盖现有的CSS属性。给定customStyleSheet字符串中定义的CSS属性仅在未在加载的文档中定义这些属性时才应用。要重置CSS，请传递空字符串作为参数。
        Parameters:
        customStyleSheet - a string that represents CSS (e.g. "body{background-color:orange;}"). Cannot be null. -代表CSS的字符串（例如）。不可能是 。
        Throws:
        java.lang.IllegalArgumentException - when customStyleSheet is null.
